setUp().notice: Set up the test suite by deploying a CheckTrue DripCheck.         This is a mock that always returns true. Alice is the owner         and also give drippie 1 ether so that it can balance transfer.

testFuzz_owner_unauthorized_reverts(addr.notice: Ensures that only the owner of Drippie can create a drip.

test_create_calledTwice_reverts().notice: Ensures that the same drip cannot be created two times.

test_create_succeeds().notice: Creates a drip and asserts that it was configured as expected.

test_drip_amount_succeeds().notice: The drip should execute and be able to transfer value.

test_drip_notExist_reverts().notice: It should revert if attempting to trigger a drip that does not exist.         Note that the drip was never created at the beginning of the test.

test_drip_reentrant_reverts().notice: A non zero interval when reentrant is true will cause a revert         when creating a drip.

test_name_notExist_reverts().notice: Attempt to update a drip that does not exist.

test_notReentrant_zeroInterval_reverts().notice: If reentrant is false and the interval is 0 then it should         revert when the drip is created.

test_not_active_reverts().notice: The owner cannot trigger the drip when it is paused.

test_reentrant_succeeds().notice: The interval must be 0 if reentrant is set on the config.

test_set_statusNone_reverts().notice: The drip status cannot be set back to NONE after it is created.

test_set_statusSame_reverts().notice: The owner cannot set the status of the drip to the status that         it is already set as.

test_set_status_succeeds().notice: The owner should be able to set the status of the drip.

test_shouldArchive_ifPaused_succeeds().notice: The owner should be able to archive the drip if it is in the         paused state.

test_shouldNotAllowActive_ifArchived_rev.notice: The owner should not be allowed to make the drip active again if         it has already been archived.

test_shouldNotAllowPaused_ifArchived_rev.notice: The owner should not be allowed to pause the drip if it         has already been archived.

test_shouldNotArchive_ifActive_reverts().notice: The owner should not be able to archive the drip if it is in the         active state.

test_status_unauthorized_reverts().notice: Expect a revert when attempting to set the status when not the owner.

test_trigger_oneFunction_succeeds().notice: A single DripAction should be able to make a state modifying call.

test_trigger_twoFunctions_succeeds().notice: Multiple drip actions should be able to be triggered with the same check.

test_twice_inOneInterval_reverts().notice: The drips can only be triggered once per interval. Attempt to         trigger the same drip multiple times in the same interval. Then         move forward to the next interval and it should trigger.
